\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F203722_88e49c4bf586f5f26422f400d3445bb2.jpg&h=14360d6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T19:25:27.000Z","msg":"佢小說話係三部曲<br />\n動畫黎計係&ldquo;物語系列&rdquo;之後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T07:18:49.000Z","msg":"印象中西尾話結物語同依家仲出緊嗰啲係外傳性質"},{"pid":"52e84028aafc35d2d007f45e42d79e9cb4b17402","tid":569831,"uid":2654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"物語系列特別係化物語真係藝術品 淨係op已經睇得出真係好俾心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1204cbd9096ae1e2a94e26142d81e6dcfec01aa8","tid":569831,"uid":133387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:53:35.000Z","msg":"大暮維人將為《化物語》繪製漫畫版 3 月 14 日起開始連載<br />\n<br />\n西尾維新的知名作品《化物語》繼日前宣布將推出漫畫連載後，今（1）日正式發表漫畫版將由知名漫畫家<span style=\"color: red;\">大暮維人</span>擔綱繪製的消息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/53/a95d7a086a01a25e0749a43d6b103455.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F53%2Fa95d7a086a01a25e0749a43d6b103455.JPG&h=8d1289a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為西尾維新「物語」系列小說第一作的化物語，故事講述高中生阿良良木曆在機緣巧合之下，無意間發現兩年中從未交流過的同班同學戰場原黑儀的秘密。為了不讓自己的秘密暴露，戰場原不斷威脅阿良良木。但實際上，阿良良木本身與戰場原一樣，隱藏著不為人知的詭異秘密。而在這個城市內，尚有更多怪物出沒&hellip;&hellip;。後續還推出了《傷物語》、《偽物語》、《貓物語》等作，並製作有電視動畫、廣播劇、遊戲以及動畫電影等作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/58/21c91c3703ae108f1d5a4831611034a5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F58%2F21c91c3703ae108f1d5a4831611034a5.JPG&h=6f43f191&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38e319bbc8a979b81a854a2ecf6ed071ac03bf22","tid":569831,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1204cbd9096ae1e2a94e26142d81e6dcfec01aa8","tid":569831,"uid":133387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:53:35.000Z","msg":"大暮維人將為《化物語》繪製漫畫版 3 月 14 日起開始連載<br />\n<br />\n西尾維新的知名作品《化物語》繼日前宣布將推出漫畫連載後，今（1）日正式發表漫畫版將由知名漫畫家<span style=\"color: red;\">大暮維人</span>擔綱繪製的消息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/53/a95d7a086a01a25e0749a43d6b103455.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F53%2Fa95d7a086a01a25e0749a43d6b103455.JPG&h=8d1289a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為西尾維新「物語」系列小說第一作的化物語，故事講述高中生阿良良木曆在機緣巧合之下，無意間發現兩年中從未交流過的同班同學戰場原黑儀的秘密。為了不讓自己的秘密暴露，戰場原不斷威脅阿良良木。但實際上，阿良良木本身與戰場原一樣，隱藏著不為人知的詭異秘密。而在這個城市內，尚有更多怪物出沒&hellip;&hellip;。後續還推出了《傷物語》、《偽物語》、《貓物語》等作，並製作有電視動畫、廣播劇、遊戲以及動畫電影等作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/58/21c91c3703ae108f1d5a4831611034a5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F58%2F21c91c3703ae108f1d5a4831611034a5.JPG&h=6f43f191&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T20:52:31.000Z","msg":"係咪物色左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁遲先出"},{"pid":"e0b6831ebce51b0e277c96a46c01ad12f235e2a8","tid":569831,"uid":126985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:37:15.000Z","msg":"成個物語系列都好正<br />\n每個人設故事都做得非常好"},{"pid":"0069a0c131b986f6cd8554681a946daae68989d7","tid":569831,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:47:01.000Z","msg":"太多"},{"pid":"e6164e86e303eeb4db51a780456d46effe224a6f","tid":569831,"uid":59159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:10:59.000Z","msg":"貝木好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2eb930c48a4b0ad68935dcdf2b5306b05c11fd","tid":569831,"uid":60151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T06:34:05.000Z","msg":"要有新房先做到個效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59032a9f175471f7373eaea4d3ca9623b4ccd456","tid":569831,"uid":62578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b2eb930c48a4b0ad68935dcdf2b5306b05c11fd","tid":569831,"uid":60151,"like"